text: José Madariaga (born 23 May 1968) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
